repository.name: TranscodeX
repository.description: TranscodeX is a Golang-based microservice application designed for multimedia transcoding and processing, specifically focused on video and image transcoding and processing. The API allows users to upload media files, specify transcoding tasks, and retrieve the processed output, all managed via AWS services like S3, ECS Fargate.
